{
  "alias": "【公共】更新RADIUS认证源",
  "case_id": 62484,
  "name": "【公共】更新RADIUS认证源",
  "description": "功能说明：该公共步骤主要用于 '【公共】更新RADIUS认证源' 操作。\n依赖入参：adIdentifySourceName2test, userPackageUuid, userTemplateUuid\n抛出变量：radiusSourceId2update, data",
